ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectOrder Terminating the Assignment of the Honourable Steven Garrett MacKinnon and Assigning the Honourable Joanne Thompson to Assist the Minister of Employment and Social Development
PrecisTerminate the assignment of the Honourable STEVEN GARRETT MACKINNON made by Order in Council P.C. 2024-896 of July 19, 2024; and assigns the Honourable JOANNE THOMPSON, Minister of State (Seniors) to be styled Minister of Employment and Social Development in the carrying out of that Minister's responsibilities.
